Achievements.Name: Highlight of the Year
Achievements.Description: Upload a photo or video to EASports.com.

Achievements.Description: In Online Dynasty, write a comment on a Dynasty Wire story.

Achievements.Name: Living Legend
Achievements.Description: Reach a coach prestige of A+ with a created coach in Dynasty (Coach Contracts on).

Achievements.Name: Dual Threat Coach
Achievements.Description: Win the BCS Championship & have the #1 recruiting class in a single season as head coach in Dynasty.

Achievements.Name: Dream Job
Achievements.Description: Become the head coach of your alma mater in Dynasty (Coach Contracts on).

Achievements.Name: Let's Do It Again
Achievements.Description: As a head coach in Dynasty, sign an extension to stay at the same school (Coach Contracts on).

Achievements.Name: Hometown Hero
Achievements.Description: Lead your alma mater to a National Championship as a head coach in Dynasty (Coach Contracts on).

Achievements.Name: Earn My Trust
Achievements.Description: Reach the max coach trust in Road to Glory Mode.

Achievements.Name: Take What's Mine
Achievements.Description: Win a position battle in Road To Glory Mode.

Achievements.Name: And the Winner Is
Achievements.Description: Win the Heisman Memorial Trophy in single team Dynasty, Road to Glory, or Heisman Challenge Mode.

Achievements.Name: Put Your Helmet On
Achievements.Description: Become a starter in Road to Glory Mode.

Achievements.Name: Future Star
Achievements.Description: Become a 5-star prospect in Road to Glory Mode.

Achievements.Name: High School Champ
Achievements.Description: Play and win the High School Championship Game in any state.

Achievements.Name: Best Class Ever
Achievements.Description: Have the #1 ranked recruiting class in a season in single team Dynasty Mode.

Achievements.Name: Unstoppable
Achievements.Description: Win a game by 35+ points on Heisman difficulty (excludes Co-Op).

Achievements.Name: Keep 'em Honest
Achievements.Description: Gain 200 rushing yards and 200 passing yards in the same game (excludes Co-Op and Road to Glory).

Achievements.Name: Up the Gut for the Score
Achievements.Description: Score a touchdown handing off to the fullback on a triple option play (excludes Co-Op).

Achievements.Name: Go for Broke
Achievements.Description: Complete a pass for 50 or more yards (excludes Co-Op).
